#4. Prompt the user for: a word, a first index, and a last index. Slice the word at the indexes provided by the user and print to the screen.
word = str(input("Give me a word: "))
ind1 = int(input("What is the first index?: "))
ind2 = int(input("What is the last index?: "))
result = word[ind1:ind2]
print(result)
